comment.name: Sample_description
comment.value: Seeds were dried after harvesting and cold-treated for minimum 7 days at 4°C  6 minutes shaking in 5% hypochloric acid, 0.05% Tween-80 solution. Subsequent washes with ddH2O (3x) and over night drying.  Cold treated seeds were surface-sterilized in 5% hypochloric acid and 0,05% Tween-80 for 6 minutes, washed and air-dried overnight. 50 seeds were sawn in a regular matrix on petri dishes containing semisolid germination medium with 0.8% agar and grown for 17 days in Percival growth chambers at 16h light/8h dark cycles and 21°C.  8 50/plate 21 °C average, 21 °C day, 21 °C night ~100% % average, ~100% % day, ~100% % night; Own medium: MS macro 50ml; B5 micro 1ml; ammonium iron citrate 50mg; sucrose 10g; MES 350mg; 8% Agar 450ml
